metadata.name: Crypto Catchers #1
metadata.description:
Algorithmically woven generative structures destined to catch ether
A self-fulfilling prophecy
Collective experiment

Note > Crypto Catchers are believed to help the accumulation of ether in the wallets of their owners.

Owners of the catchers will also receive 10,000 x 10,000 pixel image of the generated form.
